Change language of wiki: Gives you ping latency in miliseconds
Saves snippet of text in file, gives you the key. Get keys with c!keys, loads message with c!load.
Gives you summary of given query. (c!wiki [query])
Rolls a dice and gives you the result between 1 and 6. (c!roll)
Chooses between texts, texts are separated by ;. example: c!choose bla; bla1;bla2.
